---
title: Roast Duck & Chargrilled Capsicum Relish with Parmesan-Veggie Risoni & Mixed Leaf Balsamic Salad
description: Duck loves an equally rich companion and it’s going to tingle your tastebuds as you bite into its crispy skin with a smokey and sweet chargrilled capsicum relish. The light, classic combination of crisp mixed leaves and bitter Parmesan in the risoni cuts through the richness as well, giving you a dinner that’s sure to leave you feeling fancy.
